How to install:

0. Turn off Anki
1. Unzip anki-monster-pngs.zip to ~/Downloads/anki-monster-pngs
2. Install "main.py" into ~/Documents/Anki/addons/anki-monster.py
3. Edit "aqt/reviewer.py" from the Anki source, line 250 and add:
   
        runHook("answerCard", self.card, ease)
   
   It should look like

        self.mw.autosave()
        runHook("answerCard", self.card, ease)
        self.nextCard()

4. Turn on Anki
5. Click on a collection
6. Click on Tools > Monster
